{"tid":254523,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[IOS/AN] 從零開始的魔法書","createTime":"2017-05-23T09:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T16:15:14.000Z","uid":115718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e5fdc31bca8e5a56a5cf3821a7fdc31fab73a78b","tid":254523,"uid":115718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T09:09:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://blog.files.qoo-app.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/1705230704588.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.files.qoo-app.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F1705230704588.jpg&h=0b070c99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由日本 GREE 和 KADOKAWA 合作推出的智慧型手機遊戲新作《從零開始的魔法書（ゼロから始める魔法の書）》iOS/Android版今日（5月23日）正式開始配信。<br />\n<br />\n手遊版《從零開始的魔法書》將延續原作的世界觀，玩家可以在遊戲中創建自己的魔法師團，是一款正統的魔法指令型 RPG。而且，遊戲還會有由小說原作者 虎走かける 老師執筆的原創故事和新登場角色。<br />\n<br />\n《從零開始的魔法書》以架空的中世紀世界為背景，講述魔女「零」和被稱為「墮獸人」的半獸人傭兵結伴去尋找魔法書《零之書》的故事。<br />\n<br />\n為了紀念遊戲配信，如今遊戲內正在進行最多可以獲得250靈石的每日登入獎勵活動，遊戲的官方推特也同步舉辦轉推送角色聲優簽名色紙活動，有條件的玩家也可以關注一下。<br />\n<img src=\"https://blog.files.qoo-app.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/17052307063413.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.files.qoo-app.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F17052307063413.jpg&h=03584ec2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://blog.files.qoo-app.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/1705230706474.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.files.qoo-app.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F1705230706474.jpg&h=34bf04f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://blog.files.qoo-app.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/17052307065822.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.files.qoo-app.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F17052307065822.jpg&h=04f65854&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n(本文系QooApp獨家原創，如欲轉載，請註明出處 <a href=\"http://www.qoo-app.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.qoo-app.com&d=ppZu%2F4t08H3ZVi%2BcUGUaq6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=02747ada\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.qoo-app.com</a>) #6519"},{"pid":"9a2ce7b4a5fafac42a46298c788d9d7b7dba9e5b","tid":254523,"uid":115718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T09:09:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/id1212696414\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fjp%2Fapp%2Fid1212696414&d=ppZu%2F4t08H3ZVi%2BcUGUaq6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=ae6bff3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/id1212696414</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/5003\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.qoo-app.com%2Fapp%2F5003&d=ppZu%2F4t08H3ZVi%2BcUGUaq6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=20b8f821\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/5003</a>"},{"pid":"2c9f9d9515ddcb9ee17d102c59dc08771249c1f8","tid":254523,"uid":115718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T09:15:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vf1h0Eoay1Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dvf1h0Eoay1Q&d=ppZu%2F4t08H3ZVi%2BcUGUaq6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=a9152d9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vf1h0Eoay1Q</a>"},{"pid":"9fc752da55ed8f2956b63f5d63ac582c2da2ae26","tid":254523,"uid":54600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T09:19:25.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"d91906d827b90fff47c051e05a693541c8a92ad0","tid":254523,"uid":115718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T09:21:18.000Z","msg":"一開始送10抽，抽中人物有EX技就開波，有pvp"},{"pid":"af5809cab6bcfaa82a00977b1fc2a1809c8a38b9","tid":254523,"uid":31425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T11:32:09.000Z","msg":"抽完十抽果十條友係邊到拎？角色一覽同編成都冇既..."},{"pid":"2ab5abcb2e7439d6d505fcd8b3e7e9bf0e0a8cb6","tid":254523,"uid":115718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T11:33:44.000Z","msg"